nodes.text: The Quelii system was a star system in the Quelii sector.

A character in Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided states that Dathomir is located in the Quelii system, but with the release of Star Wars Galaxies: Jump to Lightspeed, the system you travel to when traveling to Dathomir is called the Dathomir system. The game still presents these two conflicting pieces of information. It is possible the developers meant sector instead of system.
